msgstr "C1 तः C6 पर्यन्तं संगृहीतं मूल्यं उपयुज्यताम्"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:647
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comments on Specific Functions"
msgstr "विशिष्टकार्यविषये टिप्पण्यानि"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:650
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mod and IntDiv"
msgstr "मोड एवं इन्टडिव"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Mod</guibutton> gives the remainder of dividing the displayed "
"number by the next input number."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Mod</guibutton> इत्यनेन प्रदर्शितसङ्ख्यायाः अग्रिमनिवेशसङ्ख्यायाः विभाजनस्य "
"अवशिष्टं भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:656
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>22 Mod 8 = </userinput> will give the result <emphasis>6</"
"emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>22 Mod 8 = </userinput> इत्यनेन <emphasis>6</emphasis> इति परिणामः "
"प्राप्यते"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>22.345 Mod 8 = </userinput> will give the result <emphasis>6.345</"
"emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>22.345 Mod 8 = </userinput> इत्यनेन <emphasis>6.345</emphasis> इति "
"परिणामः प्राप्यते"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>IntDiv</guibutton> does integer "
"division of the displayed number by the next input number."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>IntDiv</guibutton> इत्यनेन "
"प्रदर्शितसङ्ख्यायाः पूर्णाङ्कविभाजनं अग्रिमनिवेशसङ्ख्यायाः कृते भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:665
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>22 Shift IntDiv 8 = </userinput> will give the result "
"<emphasis>2</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>22 Shift IntDiv 8 = </userinput> इत्यनेन <emphasis>2</emphasis> इति "
"परिणामः प्राप्यते"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>22.345 Shift IntDiv 8 = </userinput> also gives <emphasis>2</"
"emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>22.345 Shift IntDiv 8 = </userinput> इत्यनेन <emphasis>2</emphasis> "
"इत्यपि ददाति"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:675
#, no-c-format
msgid "&percnt;"
msgstr "& percnt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Used instead of the <guibutton>=</guibutton> key, <guibutton>%</guibutton> "
"interprets the final operation carried out in the current calculation as "
"follows:"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>=</guibutton> कीलस्य स्थाने प्रयुक्तं <guibutton>%</guibutton> वर्तमानगणने "
"कृतस्य अन्तिमक्रियायाः व्याख्यां निम्नलिखितरूपेण करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the final operator is + or - the second argument is interpreted as "
"percentage of the first operand."
msgstr ""
"यदि अन्तिमः ऑपरेटरः + अथवा - भवति तर्हि द्वितीयः तर्कः प्रथमस्य ऑपरेण्ड् इत्यस्य "
"प्रतिशतरूपेण व्याख्यायते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:687
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the final operator is * divide the result of the multiplication by 100."
msgstr "यदि अन्तिमः संचालकः * अस्ति तर्हि गुणनस्य परिणामं 100 द्वारा विभजन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the final operator is / give the left operand as a percentage of the "
"right operand."
msgstr ""
"यदि अन्तिमः संचालकः / अस्ति तर्हि वाम-ऑपरेण्ड् दक्षिण-ऑपरेण्ड् इत्यस्य प्रतिशतरूपेण ददातु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:696
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In all other cases the &percnt; key gives identical results to the = key."
msgstr "अन्येषु सर्वेषु सति &percnt; कीलः = कीलस्य समानं परिणामं ददाति ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples:"
msgstr "उदाहरणानि :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>150 + 50 %</userinput> gives <emphasis>225</emphasis> (150 plus "
"50 percent of this amount)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>१५० + ५० %</userinput> इत्यनेन <emphasis>२२५</emphasis> (१५० प्लस् "
"अस्य राशिस्य ५० प्रतिशतं) प्राप्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:706
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>42 * 3 %</userinput> gives <emphasis>1.26</emphasis> (42 * 3 / "
"100)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>42 * 3 %</userinput> इत्यनेन <emphasis>1.26</emphasis> (42 * 3 / "
"100) दत्तः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>45 / 55 %</userinput> gives <emphasis>81.81...</emphasis> (45 is "
"81.81.. percent of 55)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>45 / 55 %</userinput> इत्यनेन <emphasis>81.81...</emphasis> (45 इति "
"81.81.. ५५ इत्यस्य प्रतिशतं) ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:717
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lsh and Rsh"
msgstr "लश् च ऋषः"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:720
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Lsh</guibutton> left shifts the integer part of the displayed "
"value (multiplies it by 2) n times, where n is the next input number, and "
"gives an integer result (base is set to <guibutton>Bin</guibutton>):"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Lsh</guibutton> वामभागे प्रदर्शितस्य मूल्यस्य पूर्णाङ्कभागं (2 गुणयति) n गुणान् "
"स्थानान्तरयति, यत्र n अग्रिमः निवेशसङ्ख्या अस्ति, तथा च पूर्णाङ्कपरिणामं ददाति (आधारः "
"<guibutton>Bin</ गुइबटन>): ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>10 Lsh 3 =</userinput> gives <emphasis>80</emphasis> (10 "
"multiplied by 2 three times)."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>10 Lsh 3 =</userinput> इत्यनेन <emphasis>80</emphasis> (10 गुणितं 2 "
"त्रिगुणं) प्राप्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:725
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>10.345 Lsh 3 =</userinput> also gives <emphasis>80</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>10.345 Lsh 3 =</userinput> इत्यपि <emphasis>80</emphasis> ददाति ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Rsh</guibutton> right shifts the value (performs an integer "
"divide by 2) n times."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Rsh</guibutton> दक्षिणतः मूल्यं (2 द्वारा पूर्णाङ्कविभाजनं करोति) n वारं "
"स्थानान्तरयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>16 Rsh 2 =</userinput> gives <emphasis>4</emphasis> (16 divided "
"by 2 twice)."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>16 Rsh 2 =</userinput> इत्यनेन <emphasis>4</emphasis> (16 द्विगुणं 2 "
"इत्यनेन विभक्तम्) इति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>16.999 Rsh 2 =</userinput> also gives <emphasis>4</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>16.999 Rsh 2 =</userinput> इत्यपि < emphasis>4</emphasis> ददाति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cmp, And, Or and Xor"
msgstr "Cmp, And, Or च Xor इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Cmp</guibutton>, <guibutton>And</guibutton> and "
"<guibutton>Or</guibutton> functions perform bitwise logical operations and "
"therefore appear more meaningful if the base is set to <guilabel>Hex</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Oct</guilabel> or <guilabel>Bin</guilabel> rather than "
"<guilabel>Dec</guilabel>. In the following examples base is set to "
"<guilabel>Bin</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Cmp</guibutton>, <guibutton>And</guibutton> तथा <guibutton>Or</"
"guibutton> कार्याणि बिट्विज् तार्किकक्रियाः कुर्वन्ति अतः यदि आधारः <guilabel>Hex</"
"guilabel इति सेट् भवति तर्हि अधिकं सार्थकं दृश्यते >, <guilabel>Oct</guilabel> अथवा "
"<guilabel>Bin</guilabel> न तु <guilabel>Dec</guilabel> इति । निम्नलिखित "
"उदाहरणेषु आधारः <guilabel>Bin</guilabel> इति सेट् भवति ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:754
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Cmp</guibutton> performs a 1's complement (inverts the bits)."
msgstr "<guibutton>Cmp</guibutton> 1 इत्यस्य पूरकं करोति (बिट्स् विपर्ययति) ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>101 Cmp</userinput> gives <emphasis>111...111010</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>101 Cmp</userinput> इत्यनेन <emphasis>111...111010</emphasis> इति "
"दत्तम्"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:761
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>AND</guibutton> does a logical AND."
msgstr "<guibutton>AND</guibutton> तार्किकं AND करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>101 AND 110 =</userinput> gives <emphasis>100</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>101 AND 110 =</userinput> इत्यनेन <emphasis>100</emphasis> इति दत्तम्"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:767
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>OR</guibutton> does the logical OR."
msgstr "<guibutton>OR</guibutton> तार्किकं OR करोति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>101 OR 110 =</userinput> gives <emphasis>111</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>101 OR 110 =</userinput> इत्यनेन <emphasis>111</emphasis> इति दत्तम्"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>XOR</guibutton> performs the logical XOR (exclusive OR) operation."
msgstr "<guibutton>XOR</guibutton> तार्किकं XOR (अनन्यं OR) कार्यं करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:775
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>101 XOR 110 =</userinput> gives <emphasis>11</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>101 XOR 110 =</userinput> इत्यनेन <emphasis>11</emphasis> इति दत्तम्"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:785
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "प्रश्नोत्तरम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:791
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I get e, the Euler number?"
msgstr "कथं e, Euler संख्या प्राप्नोमि ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:792
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <userinput>1 Shift e<superscript>x</superscript></userinput> in the "
"&kcalc; window, press <userinput>1 <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo> <keycap>N</keycap></userinput> on the keyboard "
"or use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Constants</guimenu><guimenuitem>Mathematics</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>1 नुदन्तु &kcalc; विण्डो, कीबोर्ड् मध्ये <userinput>1 <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo> <keycap>N</keycap></userinput> "
"नुदन्तु अथवा <menuchoice> इत्यस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु <guimenu>नित्य</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>गणित</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> मेन्यू ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:799
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I get two fixed digits after the period?"
msgstr "अवधिपश्चात् कथं द्वौ नियत-अङ्कौ प्राप्नुयाम् ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:800
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem> Configure "
"&kcalc;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> on the menu bar, this will bring up "
"the configuration dialog. Check <guilabel>Set decimal precision</guilabel> "
"and adjust the spin control so that it shows a 2."
msgstr ""
"मेनू-पट्टिकायां <menuchoice><guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem> विन्यस्य "
"&kcalc;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> इति चिनोतु, एतेन विन्याससंवादः आगच्छति । "
"<guilabel>दशमलवसटीकतां सेट् कुर्वन्तु</guilabel> इति परीक्ष्य स्पिननियन्त्रणं समायोजयन्तु "
"यथा एतत् 2 दर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:807
#, no-c-format
msgid "What about Precision?"
msgstr "किं परिशुद्धतायाः विषये ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main factor determining the precision of &kcalc; is whether your libc "
"and libmath supports the C data type <type>long double</type>. If this is "
"the case, &kcalc; will detect this at compile time and use it as its "
"fundamental data type to represent numbers."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; अस्ति यत् भवतः libc तथा libmath C दत्तांशप्रकारं <type>long double</type> "
"समर्थयति वा इति । इति चेत् &kcalc; संकलनसमये एतत् ज्ञास्यति तथा च संख्यानां "
"प्रतिनिधित्वार्थं तस्य मौलिकदत्तांशप्रकाररूपेण तस्य उपयोगं करिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:813
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adjust the <guilabel>Precision</guilabel> in &kcalc;'s <guibutton>Configure</"
"guibutton> dialog so that the above computations work correctly. I recommend "
"a precision of 14 if the fundamental data type for your copy of &kcalc; is "
"<type>long double</type>, otherwise 8 or 10."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; इत्यस्य <guibutton>Configure</guibutton> संवादे <guilabel>Precision</"
"guilabel> इत्येतत् समायोजयन्तु येन उपरिष्टाद् गणनाः सम्यक् कार्यं कुर्वन्ति । अहं 14 इत्यस्य "
"परिशुद्धतां अनुशंसयामि यदि भवतः &kcalc; इति <प्रकार>दीर्घ द्विगुण</type>, अन्यथा ८ वा "
"१० वा ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Higher precision doesn't necessarily lead to better results. Play with the "
"precision and you will see what I mean."
msgstr ""
